snippet.title: Diana Pretend Play with Princess carriage toy
snippet.description:
Diana is tired of household chores. She wants to be a princess. A little girl suddenly remembers that she has a magic wand! She dresses up in princess dress and turns a pumpkin into a beautiful carriage. Diana pretend play with princess carriage
